<plot>How to Avoid Awkward Situations offers tips on how to effectively locate, avoid, stall and escape from awkward situations. It addresses these topics from a chiefly non-confrontational point of view and gives options to those caught in such a predicament. Using a host and live examples, 'Awkward Situations' proves itself to be the number one source on avoiding and escaping techniques.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?248443</url></doc>
